# Vercel Web Analytics Installation

Successfully installed and configured Vercel Web Analytics for this Next.js App Router project.

## Changes Made

### 1. Package Installation
- **Added dependency**: `@vercel/analytics` version `^2.0.1`
- Installed using `pnpm add @vercel/analytics`
- Updated `package.json` and `pnpm-lock.yaml` with the new dependency

### 2. Analytics Component Integration
- **Modified**: `src/app/layout.tsx`
- Added import: `import { Analytics } from "@vercel/analytics/next";`
- Added `<Analytics />` component at the end of the `<body>` tag
- Placement follows Vercel's official documentation for Next.js App Router

## Implementation Details

The implementation follows the official Vercel Analytics quickstart guide (fetched from https://vercel.com/docs/analytics/quickstart on 2026-06-06):

1. **Framework Detection**: Identified this as a Next.js 16.2.6 project using App Router
2. **Package Manager**: Used pnpm (confirmed by pnpm-lock.yaml)
3. **Component Placement**: Added Analytics component in the root layout file (`app/layout.tsx`) inside the `<body>` tag, following Next.js App Router best practices
4. **Preserved Structure**: Maintained all existing code structure, imports order, and formatting conventions

## Verification Steps Completed

✓ **TypeScript Type Checking**: Passed with no errors  
✓ **ESLint**: Passed (only pre-existing warning unrelated to changes)  
✓ **Production Build**: Successfully completed (Next.js 16.2.6 with Turbopack)  
✓ **Lock File Updated**: pnpm-lock.yaml updated with new dependency tree  

## Next Steps

To enable analytics tracking:
1. Deploy this application to Vercel
2. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard (Project Settings → Analytics)
3. Analytics will automatically start tracking page views and web vitals

The Analytics component will send tracking data to `/<unique-path>/view` endpoints when users visit the site.

## Files Modified

- `package.json` - Added @vercel/analytics dependency
- `pnpm-lock.yaml` - Updated with new dependency resolution
- `src/app/layout.tsx` - Added Analytics import and component
